
<h1>Listing showblogs</h1>
<ul>
  <li>If you would like to make your OWN run please click:</li>
<li>:- new showblog -: and add your notes as you would choose.</li>
<br/>
<li>To join a run, this means you will make particular levels</li>
<li>when someone else has started, please click :- the showblog name -: and</li>
<li>add your events etc.</li>
<br/>
<li>If you make a mistake and want to delete or edit, the trusty that made it should be able to change it.</li>
<br/>
</ul>
<table class="horizontal_table" style="width: 100%; height: 10px;" border="1">
<tbody>

  <tr>
    <th width="15%"  >Player</th>
    <th width="15%"  >Name</th>
    <th width="15%" >Rundate</th>
    <th width="15%" >Spec Choice</th>
    <th width="15%">Level Range</th>
    <th width="15%">Note</th>
    <th width="5%"></th>
    <th width="5%"></th>
   
  </tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<div id="showblog-list">
<% @showblogs.each do |showblog| %>
  <table class="horizontal_table" style="width: 100%; height: 10px;" border="1" cellspacing="0">
<tbody>


  <tr valign="top" class="<%= cycle('list-line-odd', 'list-line-even') %>" >
    <td width="15%" ><%= showblog.user.try(:player) %></td>
    <td width="15%" ><%= link_to "#{showblog.name}", showblog_path(showblog) %></td>
    <td width="15%"><%= showblog.rundate.strftime("%Y-%b-%d") %></td>
    <td width="15%"><%= showblog.spec_choice %></td>
    <td width="15%"><%= showblog.level_range %></td>
    <td width="15%"><%= showblog.note %></td>
    <td width="5%"><%= link_to image_tag("ic_settings_black_24dp.png"), action: :edit, id: showblog.id %></td>
    <td width="5%"><%= link_to image_tag("ic_delete_forever.png"), showblog, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
        
  </tr>
<% end %>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<br />

<h2><%= link_to 'New Showblog', new_showblog_path %> </h2> 